title: POPPYCOCK! New Couples + Breakups
description: Welcome to poppycock! This is a new segment we're doing on the podcast where Jessi and Stew talk poppycock (nonsense) about things going on in the world, pop culture or the industry. We hope you enjoy this first episode! Short episodes coming every Tuesday. In this episode, they chat about the unlikely pairing of Kourtney Kardashian and Blink 182 drummer Travis Barker. And we also talk about the shocking (or not so shocking) break up between Bachelorette Clare Crawley and Dale Moss. Join us as we talk poppycock!
